title: Pond's Flawless White Deep Whitening Facial Foam 100 g
description:
Pond's Flawless White Deep Whitening Facial Foam brightens up skin visibly, as it cleanses and refreshes. Especially the VAO-B3 complex helps to give a naturally flawless radiant skin. 
It leaves the skin soft, smooth and sparkling clean and rids skin of dirt, oil & darkness causing impurities.
It conditions the skin, so the moisturizer can work better.

title: D.U.P Wonder Eyelid Tape Mild - 120pcs
description: D.U.P Wonder Eyelid Tape Mild - 120 pcs Keep your double eyelid for whole day Only 0.09 mm, extremely thin transparent double-sided tape. Soft and gentle feeling adhesive.

title: Basis Cleaner Clean Face Wash, 6 Ounce Tube (Pack of 4)
description: Basis Cleaner Clean Face Wash is 100% oil-free and soap-free and is designed for normal to oily skin.  It contains refreshing mint, purifying lemongrass, and  soothing aloe botanicals. The invigorating lather rinses cleanly without residue and lifts away make-up, dirt, and pollution, leaving clean, refreshed skin.
